name: Under a Blue Star
tagline: A story of times and worlds colliding...
body:
#The universe

Earth-Year 971 of the 24th era of solage II: Planet "PX842-E3" is discovered and classified as a Q-type B2 planet orbiting SX842 "blue dwarf"-type star by migratory telescope.

Earth-Year 976 of the 24th era of solage II: Pal-One Senate denies approval to PX842-E3 colonial plan and edicts a starmap removal d√©cret of the object. Senate Iondile's full statement "...What? A blue dwarf star? What is this stupid algorythm saying... Bloody stupid interns... Next!".

...And that's basically how manking ended, you can blame it on administrative paperwork!
